<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Confirm Your Registration</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .note { color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .welcome { color: #2c3e50; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<p class="welcome">Welcome, {{username}}!</p>
<p>Thank you for registering with us. To complete your registration, please verify your email address using the OTP below:</p>

<div class="otp-code">{{otpCode}}</div>

<p>This code will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
<p class="note">If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
</body>
</html>